data.title: Erwin von Witzleben
data.text:
[1] Hanging

Father: Georg von Witzleben (b. 1838, d. 1898)

Mother: Therese Brandenburg

Wife: Alma Else Margarethe Kleeberg ("Else", m. 21-May-1907, 2 children)

Daughter: Eva-Maria Edelgarde Charlotte Amalie von Witzleben (b. 1908)

Conspiracy

Treason

Tortured
